ShivaVG
------------------------------------------
ShivaVG is an open-source ANSI C implementation of the Khronos' OpenVG
specification for hardware-accelerated vector graphics API. It is built
entirely on top of OpenGL.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.7-1
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libGL1-7.8.2-1
  libGLU1-7.8.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-9-1
  automake-4-10
  binutils-2.20.51-2
  cygport-0.10.2-1
  gawk-3.1.8-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.4-3
  libtool-2.4-1
  make-3.81-2

Canonical website:
  http://shivavg.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/shivavg/ShivaVG-0.2.1.zip

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ShivaVG-0.2.1-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ShivaVG-0.2.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ShivaVG-0.2.1-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ShivaVG-0.2.1-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOpenVG0-0.2.1-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOpenVG-devel-0.2.1-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ShivaVG)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ShivaVG.README
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/README
  /usr/share/doc/ShivaVG/TODO

(libOpenVG0)
  /usr/bin/cygOpenVG-0.dll

(libOpenVG-devel)
  /usr/include/vg/openvg.h
  /usr/include/vg/vgu.h
  /usr/lib/libOpenVG.a
  /usr/lib/libOpenVG.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libOpenVG.la

